         <t:abstract>
            <t:p>The work transmitted in Gǝʿǝz as <t:foreign xml:lang="gez">Dǝrsān za-ʾabbā Yāʿqob ṗāṗṗās za-hagara Nǝṣǝbin za-kama maṣʾa nǝguśa Fārs
